reviewText: I purchased a lot of movies when they were on sale during the Christmas season.  I wanted the complete collection of Harry Potter for the grandchildren.

The Azkaban is labeled on the outside correctly but the movie that is burned on the disk is polar express.  Tom Hanks isn't in Harry Potter! lol! I purchased this at twice at two best buy locations in two separate states and had the same problem so It's obviously a manufacturers problem.
this Harry potter DVD completed the set for my granddaughter's set now she has all eight and she loves them.

when part 3 starts playing it may play the movie polar express. this is some kind of quirk. i ordered 3 copies and it happened with each. finally i googled it and found out it is happening to others. just push the menu button and it will take you to the right movie!

I had the same problem as another purchaser did. The Escape from Azkaban was actually polar express when the DVD started. I am very un happy with this purchase bc now I will have to purchase this movie separately. Waste of my time and money.

This double feature is certainly a double feature, if you want to watch a Christmas tale and Lord Voldemort. The first dvd says Prisoner of Azkaban on it, but it plays The Polar Express. The second dvd, The Goblet of Fire, is legit. But the first is a total rip off. Don't buy this DVD set. You can't even contact the seller to let them know they've made a mistake. Very angry that I've been duped, don't fall for the same trick!

I looked at a few. I am reading the books to my children and then watching movies. I didn't need extra features and this has good quality as well as 2 movies in one great price. Very helpful since I'm buying all 7.
